text: Dire situation. Not sure how much their slots at airports are worth. Probably quite a bit with our airports getting crowded. But lenders will have to take a huge haircut
author: raoabhijeet

text: Happy Holi everyone! I have mastered the back lanes of the neighborhood so I managed to go out and come back without getting any color put on me. Some kids tried to douse me with a bucket of water but missed. Next up: dodging some relatives arriving with organic colors!
author: raoabhijeet

text: After twin Boeing 737 Max crashes other countries may rely less on FAA certification and do their own aircraft safety assessments.
author: raoabhijeet

text: ‘Sacred Games’ was Ok. Had a book as an underlying text. ‘Made in Heaven’ - couldn’t get through two shows. Netflix has a Delhi Crime show - dialogue looks awful.
author: raoabhijeet

text: My advice to Amazon Prime and Netflix is don’t be in a hurry to green light Indian content. Make sure it meets universal standards of excellence. Some recent web series have been very sub par.
author: raoabhijeet

text: We should value honest and hard working politicians when we have them in our midst. Don’t mistake humbleness and dignity for lack of stature. Any day I’d rather have a Manohar Parrikar running a part of the country than some of our other entitled politicians
author: raoabhijeet

text: Really sad to hear of this. An honest and hard working leader. He maintained his composure and dignity throughout.
author: raoabhijeet

text: According to some experts Boeing should have opted for a clean sheet design rather than refreshing the 50 year old 737.
author: raoabhijeet

text: The Christchurch terrorist not only filmed his attack but also posted a lengthy manifesto espousing white supremacist ideology. And since he was caught alive he will likely use his trial to further disseminate his bigotry.
author: raoabhijeet
